article.description: — Anwar Gill had 15 points off the bench to carry La Salle to a 58-48 win over Drexel on Saturday.
article.headline: Gill scores 15 to lift La Salle past Drexel 58-48
article.linkText: Gill scores 15 to lift La Salle past Drexel 58-48
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Anwar Gill had 15 points off the bench to carry La Salle to a 58-48 win over Drexel on Saturday. David Beatty had 11 points for La Salle (2-3). Jack Clark added seven points and 13 rebounds. Jared Kimbrough had three blocks. Camren Wynter had 15 points for the Dragons (3-2). Zach Walton added 10 points. James Butler had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
